  <body dur="03:30.030">
    <div begin="00:13.730" end="03:30.030">
      <p begin="00:13.730" end="00:15.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:13.730" end="00:14.320">Oh</span> <span begin="00:14.320" end="00:14.530">on</span> <span begin="00:14.530" end="00:14.650">the</span> <span begin="00:14.750" end="00:15.930">bound</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哦 踏上这归途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哦 踏上這歸途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ 帰路について</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 귀로에 올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Oh sur le chemin du retour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah de regreso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ach auf dem Heimweg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah neste caminho de volta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Oh sulla via del ritorno</span></p>
      <p begin="00:17.770" end="00:21.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:17.770" end="00:18.410">So</span><span begin="00:18.410" end="00:18.550">ber</span> <span begin="00:18.550" end="00:18.760">and</span> <span begin="00:18.760" end="00:19.430">down</span> <span begin="00:19.540" end="00:20.350">my</span> <span begin="00:20.350" end="00:20.600">hear</span><span begin="00:20.600" end="00:20.720">t</span> <span begin="00:20.820" end="00:21.570">holds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">清醒而低落 我的心仍在坚守</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">清醒而低落 我的心仍在堅守</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">冷静に 沈む心を抱きしめる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">차분하게 가라앉은 마음을 다잡아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Lucide et abattue mon cœur s'accroche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">sobria y decaída mi corazón resiste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Klar und bedrückt hält mein Herz stand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sóbria e abatida meu coração resiste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Sobria e malinconica il mio cuore resiste</span></p>
      <p begin="00:26.930" end="00:29.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:26.930" end="00:27.520">Cir</span><span begin="00:27.520" end="00:27.590">c</span><span begin="00:27.590" end="00:27.740">ling</span> <span begin="00:27.740" end="00:27.930">a</span><span begin="00:27.930" end="00:29.320">roun</span><span begin="00:29.320" end="00:29.380">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">兜兜转转</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">兜兜轉轉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ぐるぐると巡り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">주위를 맴돌아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tournant en rond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dando vueltas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Immer im Kreis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Andando em círculos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Girando in tondo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:31.190" end="00:35.600" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:31.190" end="00:31.760">Our</span> <span begin="00:31.760" end="00:31.880">lit</span><span begin="00:31.880" end="00:32.060">tle</span> <span begin="00:32.060" end="00:32.530">town,</span> <span begin="00:32.530" end="00:32.590">i</span><span begin="00:32.590" end="00:32.710">t's</span> <span begin="00:32.710" end="00:33.340">our</span> <span begin="00:33.600" end="00:35.600">home</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这座小镇 是我们的归宿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這座小鎮 是我們的歸宿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちの小さな街 それが私たちの居場所</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리의 작은 마을, 그곳이 우리의 안식처야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Notre petite ville c'est notre foyer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nuestra pequeña ciudad, es nuestro hogar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unsere kleine Stadt sie ist unser Zuhause</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nossa pequena cidade, é o nosso lar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">La nostra piccola città è la nostra casa</span></p>
      <p begin="00:41.390" end="00:43.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:41.390" end="00:41.590">And</span> <span begin="00:41.590" end="00:41.720">there</span><span begin="00:41.720" end="00:41.800">'s</span> <span begin="00:41.800" end="00:42.220">some</span><span begin="00:42.220" end="00:42.440">thing</span> <span begin="00:42.440" end="00:42.630">'bout</span> <span begin="00:42.630" end="00:42.710">the</span> <span begin="00:42.710" end="00:42.920">c</span><span begin="00:42.920" end="00:43.080">i</span><span begin="00:43.080" end="00:43.250">ty</span> <span begin="00:43.250" end="00:43.620">ligh</span><span begin="00:43.850" end="00:43.970">ts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">城市的灯火 总是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">城市的燈火 總是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">街の灯りには特別な何かがある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도시의 불빛에는 무언가 특별한 게 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et il y a quelque chose dans les lumières de la ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y hay algo sobre las luces de la ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und die Lichter der Stadt haben etwas Besonderes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E tem algo nas luzes da cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">E c'è qualcosa nelle luci della città</span></p>
      <p begin="00:44.730" end="00:47.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:44.730" end="00:44.950">Been</span> <span begin="00:44.950" end="00:45.170">a</span> <span begin="00:45.170" end="00:45.430">long</span> <span begin="00:45.550" end="00:45.860">time</span> <span begin="00:45.990" end="00:46.240">co</span><span begin="00:46.390" end="00:46.570">ming</span> <span begin="00:46.570" end="00:46.860">to</span> <span begin="00:46.860" end="00:47.240">re</span><span begin="00:47.240" end="00:47.460">a</span><span begin="00:47.460" end="00:47.740">li</span><span begin="00:47.740" end="00:47.790">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">历经漫长岁月 才终于恍然明了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">歷經漫長歲月 才終於恍然明瞭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">気づくまでに長い時間がかかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">깨닫기까지 참 오랜 시간이 걸렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il a fallu si longtemps pour s'en rendre compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ha pasado mucho tiempo para darme cuenta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hat lange gedauert bis ich es erkannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levou muito tempo até eu perceber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ci è voluto tanto tempo per capirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:48.060" end="00:50.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:48.060" end="00:48.270">I</span> <span begin="00:48.270" end="00:48.510">don't</span> <span begin="00:48.510" end="00:48.840">know</span> <span begin="00:48.840" end="00:48.970">i</span><span begin="00:48.970" end="00:49.090">f</span> <span begin="00:49.090" end="00:49.200">I</span> <span begin="00:49.200" end="00:49.440">should</span> <span begin="00:49.440" end="00:49.940">say</span> <span begin="00:49.940" end="00:50.310">thi</span><span begin="00:50.310" end="00:50.520">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知我是否该 将此诉诸于口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知我是否該 將此訴諸於口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これを言うべきか分からない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 말을 해도 될지 모르겠어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas si je devrais le dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé si debería decir esto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht ob ich das sagen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei se eu deveria dizer isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non so se dovrei dirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:51.360" end="00:55.960" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:51.360" end="00:51.480">Cau</span><span begin="00:51.480" end="00:51.580">se</span> <span begin="00:51.580" end="00:51.890">I</span> <span begin="00:51.890" end="00:52.280">real</span><span begin="00:52.280" end="00:52.670">ly</span> <span begin="00:52.670" end="00:53.070">want</span> <span begin="00:53.070" end="00:53.290">to</span> <span begin="00:53.290" end="00:53.390">be</span> <span begin="00:53.390" end="00:53.530">s</span><span begin="00:53.530" end="00:55.960">trong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为我只愿 展现坚强的模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為我只願 展現堅強的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だって本当は強くありたいから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 정말 강한 사람이고 싶으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car je veux vraiment être forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque de verdad quiero ser fuerte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn ich will wirklich stark sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque eu realmente quero ser forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Perché voglio davvero essere forte</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.020" end="01:02.900" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:57.020" end="00:57.430">Li</span><span begin="00:57.430" end="00:57.590">fe</span> <span begin="00:57.590" end="00:57.710">i</span><span begin="00:57.710" end="00:57.870">s</span> <span begin="00:57.870" end="00:58.370">bet</span><span begin="00:58.370" end="00:58.700">ter</span> <span begin="00:58.700" end="00:59.440">wi</span><span begin="00:59.440" end="00:59.520">th</span> <span begin="00:59.520" end="00:59.890">you</span> <span begin="01:00.150" end="01:00.370">a</span><span begin="01:00.370" end="01:02.900">round</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有你在身旁 这人生才更美好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有你在身旁 這人生才更美好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたが側にいてくれる人生の方がいい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 곁에 있는 삶이 더 나아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vie est plus belle quand tu es là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vida es mejor contigo cerca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Leben ist besser mit dir an meiner Seite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A vida é melhor com você por perto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">La vita è migliore con te accanto</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.730" end="01:08.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:05.730" end="01:05.960">Af</span><span begin="01:05.960" end="01:06.260">ter</span> <span begin="01:06.260" end="01:06.440">e</span><span begin="01:06.440" end="01:06.560">ve</span><span begin="01:06.560" end="01:06.740">ry</span><span begin="01:06.860" end="01:07.090">thing</span> <span begin="01:07.090" end="01:07.220">you</span> <span begin="01:07.350" end="01:07.780">ga</span><span begin="01:07.780" end="01:07.880">ve</span> <span begin="01:07.980" end="01:08.320">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在你赋予我了一切之后</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在你賦予我了一切之後</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたが全てをくれたのに</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 내게 모든 걸 주었는데도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Après tout ce que tu m'as donné</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Después de todo lo que me diste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nach allem was du mir gegeben hast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Depois de tudo que você me deu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Dopo tutto quello che mi hai dato</span></p>
