      <p begin="01:10.340" end="01:12.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:10.340" end="01:10.520">I</span> <span begin="01:10.520" end="01:10.660">s</span><span begin="01:10.660" end="01:10.810">till</span> <span begin="01:10.910" end="01:11.110">play</span><span begin="01:11.110" end="01:11.180">ed</span> <span begin="01:11.180" end="01:11.460">hide</span> <span begin="01:11.460" end="01:11.880">and</span> <span begin="01:11.880" end="01:12.360">see</span><span begin="01:12.360" end="01:12.440">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我却仍在与你 玩着捉迷藏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我卻仍在與你 玩著捉迷藏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私はまだ かくれんぼをしていた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 여전히 숨바꼭질만 하고 있었지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je jouais encore à cache-cache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo aún jugaba a las escondidas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Habe ich immer noch Verstecken gespielt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu ainda brincava de esconde-esconde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Giocavo ancora a nascondino</span></p>
      <p begin="01:12.440" end="01:14.950" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:12.440" end="01:12.610">Woul</span><span begin="01:12.610" end="01:12.740">dn't</span> <span begin="01:12.850" end="01:13.110">blame</span> <span begin="01:13.300" end="01:13.530">you</span> <span begin="01:13.530" end="01:13.650">i</span><span begin="01:13.650" end="01:13.730">f</span> <span begin="01:13.730" end="01:13.890">you</span> <span begin="01:14.030" end="01:14.530">hate</span> <span begin="01:14.680" end="01:14.950">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若你怨恨我 我也毫无怨言</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若你怨恨我 我也毫無怨言</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を憎んだとしても 責めたりしない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 날 미워해도 탓하지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne t'en voudrais pas si tu me détestais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No te culparía si me odias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würde es dir nicht verübeln wenn du mich hasst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não te culparia se você me odiasse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non ti biasimerei se mi odiassi</span></p>
      <p begin="01:15.570" end="01:16.590" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:15.570" end="01:16.090">May</span><span begin="01:16.330" end="01:16.590">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">或许吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">或許吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">もしかしたら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어쩌면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peut-être</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vielleicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Talvez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Forse</span></p>
      <p begin="01:17.000" end="01:19.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:17.000" end="01:17.420">Soon</span> <span begin="01:17.420" end="01:17.670">you</span> <span begin="01:17.670" end="01:17.920">and</span> <span begin="01:17.920" end="01:18.050">I</span> <span begin="01:18.160" end="01:18.510">could</span> <span begin="01:18.680" end="01:19.080">mee</span><span begin="01:19.080" end="01:19.110">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不久后 你我便能重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不久後 你我便能重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">すぐに私たち 会えるかもしれない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">머지않아 우리가 다시 만날지도 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que bientôt toi et moi pourrions nous retrouver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pronto tú y yo podríamos encontrarnos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Könnten du und ich uns bald treffen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Logo você e eu poderíamos nos encontrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Presto potremmo rivederci</span></p>
      <p begin="01:19.110" end="01:21.630" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:19.110" end="01:19.330">I</span> <span begin="01:19.330" end="01:19.420">would</span> <span begin="01:19.530" end="01:19.800">tell</span> <span begin="01:19.930" end="01:20.110">you</span> <span begin="01:20.110" end="01:20.310">that</span> <span begin="01:20.310" end="01:20.460">I'm</span> <span begin="01:20.460" end="01:20.700">s</span><span begin="01:20.700" end="01:21.260">or</span><span begin="01:21.260" end="01:21.630">ry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我会对你诉说 我的歉意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我會對你訴說 我的歉意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そうしたら ごめんなさいって伝えるよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그땐 미안하다고 말할게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je te dirais que je suis désolée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te diría que lo siento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würde ich dir sagen dass es mir leid tut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu te diria que sinto muito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ti direi che mi dispiace</span></p>
      <p begin="01:22.280" end="01:23.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:22.280" end="01:22.390">S</span><span begin="01:22.390" end="01:22.930">or</span><span begin="01:22.930" end="01:23.130">ry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">满心抱歉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">滿心抱歉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ごめんね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미안해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Désolée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo siento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es tut mir leid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto muito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Mi dispiace</span></p>
      <p begin="01:23.760" end="01:26.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:23.760" end="01:24.040">Pro</span><span begin="01:24.040" end="01:24.200">mi</span><span begin="01:24.200" end="01:24.330">se</span> <span begin="01:24.330" end="01:24.590">I'll</span> <span begin="01:24.590" end="01:24.770">le</span><span begin="01:24.770" end="01:24.880">t</span> <span begin="01:24.880" end="01:25.260">you</span> <span begin="01:25.260" end="01:25.510">s</span><span begin="01:25.620" end="01:26.320">pea</span><span begin="01:26.320" end="01:26.380">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我承诺 这次会静静听你诉说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我承諾 這次會靜靜聽你訴說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">今度はあなたの話を聞くって約束する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 이야기를 듣겠다고 약속할게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je promets de te laisser parler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Prometo que te dejaré hablar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verspreche dass ich dich reden lasse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Prometo que vou te deixar falar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Prometto che ti lascerò parlare</span></p>
      <p begin="01:26.000" end="01:28.010" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:26.000" end="01:26.420">Pro</span><span begin="01:26.420" end="01:26.540">mi</span><span begin="01:26.540" end="01:26.650">se</span> <span begin="01:26.650" end="01:26.850">I</span> <span begin="01:26.850" end="01:27.070">could</span> <span begin="01:27.070" end="01:27.440">go</span> <span begin="01:27.440" end="01:28.010">there</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我承诺 我会走向你的身边</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我承諾 我會走向你的身邊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そこへ行くって約束する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그곳으로 가겠다고 약속할게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je promets de m'y rendre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Prometo que podré ir allí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verspreche dass ich dorthin gehen könnte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Prometo que irei até aí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Prometto che verrò da te</span></p>
      <p begin="01:34.730" end="01:37.370" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:34.730" end="01:34.930">And</span> <span begin="01:34.930" end="01:35.060">there</span><span begin="01:35.060" end="01:35.130">'s</span> <span begin="01:35.130" end="01:35.410">some</span><span begin="01:35.560" end="01:35.780">thing</span> <span begin="01:35.780" end="01:35.970">'bout</span> <span begin="01:35.970" end="01:36.040">the</span> <span begin="01:36.040" end="01:36.250">c</span><span begin="01:36.250" end="01:36.420">i</span><span begin="01:36.420" end="01:36.590">ty</span> <span begin="01:36.590" end="01:36.950">ligh</span><span begin="01:37.190" end="01:37.370">ts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">城市的灯火 总是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">城市的燈火 總是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">街の灯りには特別な何かがある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도시의 불빛에는 무언가 특별한 게 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et il y a quelque chose dans les lumières de la ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y hay algo sobre las luces de la ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und die Lichter der Stadt haben etwas Besonderes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E tem algo nas luzes da cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">E c'è qualcosa nelle luci della città</span></p>
      <p begin="01:38.070" end="01:41.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:38.070" end="01:38.290">Been</span> <span begin="01:38.290" end="01:38.510">a</span> <span begin="01:38.510" end="01:38.710">long</span> <span begin="01:38.890" end="01:39.160">time</span> <span begin="01:39.330" end="01:39.570">co</span><span begin="01:39.730" end="01:39.910">ming</span> <span begin="01:39.910" end="01:40.200">to</span> <span begin="01:40.200" end="01:40.580">re</span><span begin="01:40.580" end="01:40.800">a</span><span begin="01:40.800" end="01:41.080">li</span><span begin="01:41.080" end="01:41.130">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">历经漫长岁月 才终于恍然明了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">歷經漫長歲月 才終於恍然明瞭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">気づくまでに長い時間がかかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">깨닫기까지 참 오랜 시간이 걸렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il a fallu si longtemps pour s'en rendre compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ha pasado mucho tiempo para darme cuenta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hat lange gedauert bis ich es erkannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levou muito tempo até eu perceber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ci è voluto tanto tempo per capirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:41.420" end="01:43.750" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:41.420" end="01:41.630">I</span> <span begin="01:41.630" end="01:41.870">don't</span> <span begin="01:41.870" end="01:42.200">know</span> <span begin="01:42.200" end="01:42.330">i</span><span begin="01:42.330" end="01:42.440">f</span> <span begin="01:42.440" end="01:42.560">I</span> <span begin="01:42.560" end="01:42.800">should</span> <span begin="01:42.800" end="01:43.320">say</span> <span begin="01:43.320" end="01:43.650">thi</span><span begin="01:43.650" end="01:43.750">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知我是否该 将此诉诸于口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知我是否該 將此訴諸於口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これを言うべきか分からない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 말을 해도 될지 모르겠어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas si je devrais le dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé si debería decir esto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht ob ich das sagen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei se eu deveria dizer isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non so se dovrei dirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:44.700" end="01:49.290" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:44.700" end="01:44.790">Cau</span><span begin="01:44.790" end="01:44.910">se</span> <span begin="01:44.910" end="01:45.220">I</span> <span begin="01:45.220" end="01:45.610">real</span><span begin="01:45.610" end="01:46.000">ly</span> <span begin="01:46.000" end="01:46.400">want</span> <span begin="01:46.400" end="01:46.620">to</span> <span begin="01:46.620" end="01:46.720">be</span> <span begin="01:46.720" end="01:46.860">s</span><span begin="01:46.860" end="01:49.290">trong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为我只愿 展现坚强的模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為我只願 展現堅強的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だって本当は強くありたいから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 정말 강한 사람이고 싶으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car je veux vraiment être forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque de verdad quiero ser fuerte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn ich will wirklich stark sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque eu realmente quero ser forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Perché voglio davvero essere forte</span></p>
      <p begin="01:50.340" end="01:56.310" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:50.340" end="01:50.750">Li</span><span begin="01:50.750" end="01:50.910">fe</span> <span begin="01:50.910" end="01:51.040">i</span><span begin="01:51.040" end="01:51.110">s</span> <span begin="01:51.210" end="01:51.690">bet</span><span begin="01:51.690" end="01:52.100">ter</span> <span begin="01:52.100" end="01:52.760">wi</span><span begin="01:52.760" end="01:52.840">th</span> <span begin="01:52.840" end="01:53.230">you</span> <span begin="01:53.490" end="01:53.740">a</span><span begin="01:53.740" end="01:56.310">round</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有你在身旁 这人生才更美好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有你在身旁 這人生才更美好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたが側にいてくれる人生の方がいい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 곁에 있는 삶이 더 나아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vie est plus belle quand tu es là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vida es mejor contigo cerca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Leben ist besser mit dir an meiner Seite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A vida é melhor com você por perto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">La vita è migliore con te accanto</span></p>
      <p begin="02:01.410" end="02:05.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:01.410" end="02:01.600">And</span> <span begin="02:01.600" end="02:01.720">there</span><span begin="02:01.720" end="02:01.800">'s</span> <span begin="02:01.800" end="02:02.090">some</span><span begin="02:02.220" end="02:02.450">thing</span> <span begin="02:02.450" end="02:02.640">'bout</span> <span begin="02:02.640" end="02:02.710">the</span> <span begin="02:02.710" end="02:02.900">c</span><span begin="02:02.900" end="02:03.080">i</span><span begin="02:03.080" end="02:03.270">ty</span> <span begin="02:03.270" end="02:03.560">light</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">城市的灯火 总是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">城市的燈火 總是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">街の灯りには特別な何かがある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도시의 불빛에는 무언가 특별한 게 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et il y a quelque chose dans la lumière de la ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y hay algo sobre la luz de la ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und das Licht der Stadt hat etwas Besonderes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E tem algo nas luzes da cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">E c'è qualcosa nella luce della città</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:03.470" end="02:05.560"><span begin="02:03.470" end="02:03.760">(Some</span><span begin="02:03.910" end="02:04.140">thing</span> <span begin="02:04.140" end="02:04.260">'bout</span> <span begin="02:04.340" end="02:04.420">the</span> <span begin="02:04.420" end="02:04.590">c</span><span begin="02:04.590" end="02:04.750">i</span><span begin="02:04.750" end="02:05.000">ty</span> <span begin="02:05.000" end="02:05.390">ligh</span><span begin="02:05.450" end="02:05.560">ts)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这城市的灯火 总是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這城市的燈火 總是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">街の灯りには特別な何かが</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도시의 불빛에는 무언가 특별한 게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelque chose dans les lumières de la ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Algo sobre las luces de la ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Etwas Besonderes an den Lichtern der Stadt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Algo nas luzes da cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Qualcosa nelle luci della città</span></span></p>
      <p begin="02:04.730" end="02:07.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:04.730" end="02:04.950">Been</span> <span begin="02:04.950" end="02:05.170">a</span> <span begin="02:05.170" end="02:05.390">long</span> <span begin="02:05.560" end="02:05.820">time</span> <span begin="02:06.000" end="02:06.230">co</span><span begin="02:06.390" end="02:06.570">ming</span> <span begin="02:06.570" end="02:06.860">to</span> <span begin="02:06.860" end="02:07.240">re</span><span begin="02:07.240" end="02:07.470">a</span><span begin="02:07.470" end="02:07.740">li</span><span begin="02:07.740" end="02:07.780">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">历经漫长岁月 才终于恍然明了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">歷經漫長歲月 才終於恍然明瞭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">気づくまでに長い時間がかかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">깨닫기까지 참 오랜 시간이 걸렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il a fallu si longtemps pour s'en rendre compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ha pasado mucho tiempo para darme cuenta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es hat lange gedauert bis ich es erkannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levou muito tempo até eu perceber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ci è voluto tanto tempo per capirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:08.070" end="02:11.550" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:08.070" end="02:08.280">I</span> <span begin="02:08.280" end="02:08.520">don't</span> <span begin="02:08.520" end="02:08.860">know</span> <span begin="02:08.860" end="02:08.980">i</span><span begin="02:08.980" end="02:09.140">f</span> <span begin="02:09.140" end="02:09.240">I</span> <span begin="02:09.240" end="02:09.490">should</span> <span begin="02:09.490" end="02:10.000">say</span> <span begin="02:10.000" end="02:10.330">this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知我是否该 将此诉诸于口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知我是否該 將此訴諸於口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これを言うべきか分からない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 말을 해도 될지 모르겠어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas si je devrais le dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé si debería decir esto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht ob ich das sagen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei se eu deveria dizer isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non so se dovrei dirlo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:09.750" end="02:11.550"><span begin="02:09.750" end="02:09.970">(I</span> <span begin="02:09.970" end="02:10.190">don't</span> <span begin="02:10.190" end="02:10.580">know</span> <span begin="02:10.580" end="02:10.700">i</span><span begin="02:10.700" end="02:10.790">f</span> <span begin="02:10.790" end="02:10.930">I</span> <span begin="02:10.960" end="02:11.080">should</span> <span begin="02:11.160" end="02:11.550">say)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知我是否该 诉说出口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知我是否該 訴說出口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">言うべきか分からない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 말을 해도 될지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas si je devrais dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé si debería decirlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht ob ich sagen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei se eu deveria dizer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non so se dovrei</span></span></p>
