      <p begin="02:49.760" end="02:52.060" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="02:49.760" end="02:49.890">I</span><span begin="02:49.890" end="02:49.990">s</span> <span begin="02:49.990" end="02:50.190">it</span> <span begin="02:50.190" end="02:50.650">real</span><span begin="02:50.650" end="02:50.930">ly</span> <span begin="02:51.080" end="02:51.440">wan</span><span begin="02:51.440" end="02:51.670">t</span> <span begin="02:51.670" end="02:52.060">me?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你真的还需要我吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你真的還需要我嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">本当に私を求めているの？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정말 나를 원하는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Me veux-tu vraiment ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿De verdad me quieres?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Willst du mich wirklich?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você realmente me quer?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Mi vuoi davvero?</span></p>
