      <p begin="03:03.210" end="03:05.470" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="03:03.210" end="03:03.330">I</span><span begin="03:03.330" end="03:03.390">s</span> <span begin="03:03.390" end="03:03.640">it</span> <span begin="03:03.640" end="03:03.990">real</span><span begin="03:03.990" end="03:04.270">ly</span> <span begin="03:04.440" end="03:04.770">wan</span><span begin="03:04.770" end="03:05.030">t</span> <span begin="03:05.030" end="03:05.470">me?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你真的还需要我吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你真的還需要我嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">本当に私を求めているの？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정말 나를 원하는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Me veux-tu vraiment ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿De verdad me quieres?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Willst du mich wirklich?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você realmente me quer?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Mi vuoi davvero?</span></p>
      <p begin="03:05.850" end="03:07.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="03:05.850" end="03:06.300">Ay-</span><span begin="03:06.300" end="03:06.680">yeah</span> <span begin="03:06.680" end="03:07.490">ay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 是啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 是啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ そう ああ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아 예 아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah-ouais ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ay sí ay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah-ja ach</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah-yeah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ah-sì ah</span></p>
      <p begin="03:08.110" end="03:10.870" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="03:08.110" end="03:08.280">And</span> <span begin="03:08.280" end="03:08.380">there</span><span begin="03:08.380" end="03:08.480">'s</span> <span begin="03:08.480" end="03:08.790">some</span><span begin="03:08.940" end="03:09.160">thing</span> <span begin="03:09.160" end="03:09.270">'bout</span> <span begin="03:09.270" end="03:09.380">the</span> <span begin="03:09.380" end="03:09.600">c</span><span begin="03:09.600" end="03:09.800">i</span><span begin="03:09.800" end="03:09.990">ty</span> <span begin="03:09.990" end="03:10.320">ligh</span><span begin="03:10.690" end="03:10.870">ts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">城市的灯火 总是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">城市的燈火 總是惹人遐思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">街の灯りには特別な何かがある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도시의 불빛에는 무언가 특별한 게 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et il y a quelque chose dans les lumières de la ville</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y hay algo sobre las luces de la ciudad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und die Lichter der Stadt haben etwas Besonderes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E tem algo nas luzes da cidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">E c'è qualcosa nelle luci della città</span></p>
      <p begin="03:11.840" end="03:14.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="03:11.840" end="03:12.120">Long</span> <span begin="03:12.220" end="03:12.520">time</span> <span begin="03:12.680" end="03:13.130">co</span><span begin="03:13.130" end="03:13.320">ming</span> <span begin="03:13.320" end="03:13.530">to</span> <span begin="03:13.530" end="03:13.950">re</span><span begin="03:13.950" end="03:14.200">a</span><span begin="03:14.200" end="03:14.740">li</span><span begin="03:14.740" end="03:14.790">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">漫长岁月后 才终于明了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漫長歲月後 才終於明瞭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">気づくまでに長い時間がかかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">깨닫기까지 오랜 시간이 걸렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il a fallu longtemps pour s'en rendre compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mucho tiempo para darme cuenta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lange gedauert bis ich es erkannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levou muito tempo até eu perceber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Tanto tempo per capirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="03:14.810" end="03:17.300" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="03:14.810" end="03:14.970">I</span> <span begin="03:14.970" end="03:15.240">don't</span> <span begin="03:15.240" end="03:15.590">know</span> <span begin="03:15.590" end="03:15.730">i</span><span begin="03:15.730" end="03:15.840">f</span> <span begin="03:15.840" end="03:15.960">I</span> <span begin="03:15.960" end="03:16.040">should</span> <span begin="03:16.140" end="03:16.310">s</span><span begin="03:16.310" end="03:16.680">ay</span> <span begin="03:16.680" end="03:16.960">thi</span><span begin="03:17.180" end="03:17.300">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知我是否该 将此诉诸于口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不知我是否該 將此訴諸於口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これを言うべきか分からない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 말을 해도 될지 모르겠어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais pas si je devrais le dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé si debería decir esto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht ob ich das sagen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei se eu deveria dizer isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Non so se dovrei dirlo</span></p>
      <p begin="03:18.080" end="03:22.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="03:18.080" end="03:18.170">Cau</span><span begin="03:18.170" end="03:18.320">se</span> <span begin="03:18.320" end="03:18.650">I</span> <span begin="03:18.650" end="03:19.000">real</span><span begin="03:19.000" end="03:19.400">ly</span> <span begin="03:19.400" end="03:19.790">want</span> <span begin="03:19.790" end="03:20.010">to</span> <span begin="03:20.010" end="03:20.130">be</span> <span begin="03:20.130" end="03:20.410">s</span><span begin="03:20.410" end="03:22.280">trong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为我只愿 展现坚强的模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為我只願 展現堅強的模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だって本当は強くありたいから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 정말 강한 사람이고 싶으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car je veux vraiment être forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque de verdad quiero ser fuerte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn ich will wirklich stark sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque eu realmente quero ser forte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Perché voglio davvero essere forte</span></p>
